---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="OpenClaw 新闻资讯 - 龙虾助理">
  <h1>📰 OpenClaw 新闻资讯</h1>
  <p class="lead">追踪 OpenClaw 和 AI 助理领域的最新动态</p>

  <div class="news-filters">
    <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">全部</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="security">安全提醒</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="official">官方动态</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="community">社区新闻</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="industry">行业资讯</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="tutorial">教程更新</button>
  </div>

  <div class="news-list">
    <!-- 最新文章 -->
    <article class="news-card" data-category="security">
      <div class="news-meta">
        <span class="news-tag security">安全月报</span>
        <time datetime="2026-03-31">2026-03-31</time>
      </div>
      <h3>🦞 安全养虾月报 2026-03：这些隐患你注意了吗？</h3>
